title: Leopard found dead in Ududumbara
body_lines: COLOMBO (News 1st); A leopard had died after it was knocked down by a vehicle early this morning in Udu-Dumbara along the Kandy – Mahiyanganaya Road.
The carcass of the leopard was moved to the Daagawilla Forest Office for an investigation.
